Description: Cortex Linux full installation - AI-powered server management
 This meta-package installs the complete Cortex Linux system with
 all recommended packages for server management, containers, monitoring,
 and GPU support.
 .
 Includes:
  - Everything in cortex-core
  - Docker and container tools
  - Network security (nftables, fail2ban)
  - Monitoring (Prometheus node exporter)
  - Web server (nginx) and TLS (certbot)
  - Database clients (PostgreSQL, Redis, SQLite)
  - Storage tools (rsync, rclone, smartmontools)
  - Modern CLI tools (htop, btop, fzf, ripgrep, bat)
 .
 For GPU support, install the appropriate driver package:
  - NVIDIA: nvidia-driver
  - AMD: firmware-amd-graphics
